I'm doing this for your own good.

285
00:12:12,750 --> 00:12:15,000
Do you know how many people want

286
00:12:15,010 --> 00:12:16,910
to get close to our Su family now,

287
00:12:17,630 --> 00:12:18,600
and go to great lengths

288
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:20,270
to become our Su family's son-in-law?

289
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:23,200
A poor man like this

290
00:12:23,510 --> 00:12:26,120
is the best
at fooling little girls like you.

291
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:27,440
Aunt Bai,

292
00:12:27,510 --> 00:12:28,670
Jianhao is not that kind of person.

293
00:12:28,670 --> 00:12:29,910
Don't think of him like that.

294
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,720
Besides, it's Wan'er
who's looking for a boyfriend,

295
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:33,870
so let her choose the one she likes.

296
00:12:33,870 --> 00:12:34,710
Lili,

297
00:12:35,330 --> 00:12:37,030
although you're not my daughter,

298
00:12:37,340 --> 00:12:38,360
you and Wan'er are sisters

299
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:40,430
of the same father.

300
00:12:40,790 --> 00:12:42,440
Even though your father has passed away,

301
00:12:42,860 --> 00:12:45,250
you have to take care of your sister.

302
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:46,490
How can you bear

303
00:12:46,500 --> 00:12:47,890
to see her jump into the fire?

304
00:12:47,900 --> 00:12:48,910
It's none of Sister's business!

305
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:51,600
(It turns out they are half-sisters.)

306
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:53,200
Aunt Bai,

307
00:12:53,390 --> 00:12:54,320
by marrying Wan'er

308
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:56,270
to that playboy
from Chase Rodford family,

309
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:58,200
aren't you letting her
jump into the fire?

310
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:59,630
The Chase Rodford family

311
00:12:59,630 --> 00:13:01,720
is the world's top consortium.

312
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:03,720
Even the Su family is nothing

313
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:05,270
compared to them.

314
00:13:05,550 --> 00:13:06,390
You're comparing him

315
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:08,510
to the Chase Rodford family?

316
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:09,560
What a joke.

317
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:10,680
I don't care,

318
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:11,630
and I'm not afraid.

319
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:13,080
Don't think

320
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:15,170
I don't know what you're up to

321
00:13:15,180 --> 00:13:16,480
with this betrothal banquet.

322
00:13:16,750 --> 00:13:17,870
Let me tell you,

323
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:20,320
I've already decided
on Wan'er's marriage.

324
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:21,190
None of you

325
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:22,840
can ruin it for me.

326
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:25,000
And you,

327
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,150
if you hadn't secretly

328
00:13:26,150 --> 00:13:27,670
urged Wan'er in the past two years

329
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:30,550
and taken the liberty
of bringing her to Chongjiang,

330
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:32,120
she would have finished

331
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:34,790
her engagement
with the Chase Rodford family long ago.

332
00:13:35,030 --> 00:13:35,870
Aunt Bai,

333
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:37,480
Wan'er is also my sister.

334
00:13:37,750 --> 00:13:39,240
I hope she can be happy.

335
00:13:40,510 --> 00:13:42,870
Is it possible to be happy
with a poor boy?

336
00:13:42,910 --> 00:13:43,910
Look at him.

337
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:46,160
He's meeting the elders
for the first time,

338
00:13:46,160 --> 00:13:47,270
and he's empty-handed.

339
00:13:47,390 --> 00:13:48,840
How can he be polite?

340
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:50,320
Aunt, I've brought a gift.

341
00:13:51,510 --> 00:13:53,360
(Luckily, I asked Mr. Mo
to prepare a gift in advance.)

342
00:13:58,600 --> 00:14:00,200
(This stone looks
like a superb piece of stone.)

343
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:02,200
(Mr. Mo is very thoughtful.)

344
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:07,030
In all my years in the Su family,

345
00:14:07,270 --> 00:14:08,790
I've never seen

346
00:14:08,790 --> 00:14:10,550
anything so cheap.

347
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:12,240
A gift?

348
00:14:12,650 --> 00:14:14,320
That's what you're trying
to fool me with?

349
00:14:14,590 --> 00:14:15,480
Aunt,

350
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:16,960
this stone may be small,

351
00:14:16,960 --> 00:14:18,160
but its market value isn't low.

352
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,840
Why don't you take another look?

353
00:14:20,300 --> 00:14:21,990
Are you saying I don't know
what I'm talking about?

354
00:14:22,670 --> 00:14:24,080
That's not what I meant.

355
00:14:24,270 --> 00:14:25,270
- He...
- Aunt,

356
00:14:25,870 --> 00:14:26,910
what kind of stuff?

357
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:28,550
Let me have a look.

358
00:14:28,750 --> 00:14:29,720
Ge, you're here.

359
00:14:30,120 --> 00:14:32,200
It's just a piece of junk,

360
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:33,440
nothing to see.

361
00:14:35,670 --> 00:14:36,510
Wait.

362
00:14:37,630 --> 00:14:39,870
(This is the top stone
that recently sold)

363
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:42,080
(for over 100 million yuan
at Sotheby's.)

364
00:14:42,630 --> 00:14:44,320
(How come this kid has it?)

365
00:14:46,270 --> 00:14:47,110
Aunt,

366
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:49,600
since he's here to give you a gift,

367
00:14:49,620 --> 00:14:50,940
take it whether it's good or bad,

368
00:14:51,030 --> 00:14:52,120
and show him mercy.

369
00:14:53,080 --> 00:14:55,270
Ge, why do you speak for outsiders too?

370
00:14:55,270 --> 00:14:56,670
Are you still a member
of the Bai family?

371
00:14:56,670 --> 00:14:57,510
I...

372
00:14:58,440 --> 00:14:59,280
Young man,

373
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:01,390
don't you understand what I'm saying?

374
00:15:01,390 --> 00:15:02,270
I'm telling you,

375
00:15:02,270 --> 00:15:04,150
don't bother my daughter again!

376
00:15:04,550 --> 00:15:05,510
No, Aunt.

377
00:15:07,630 --> 00:15:08,470
In the Su family,

378
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:10,360
there's nothing I can't do.

379
00:15:10,800 --> 00:15:12,380
(Such a good stone.)

380
00:15:12,790 --> 00:15:14,510
(Mr. Mo, you're too generous.)

381
00:15:14,700 --> 00:15:17,240
(I should have left it to Black Tortoise
to exchange for energy.)

382
00:15:18,120 --> 00:15:19,510
Mom, you've gone too far!

383
00:15:20,270 --> 00:15:21,110
Aunt Bai,

384
00:15:21,140 --> 00:15:22,240
it's a token of his appreciation.

385
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:23,550
Aren't you going too far?

386
00:15:23,670 --> 00:15:25,360
How dare you accuse me

387
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:26,910
of something so trivial?

388
00:15:26,910 --> 00:15:27,750
Aunt,

389
00:15:28,030 --> 00:15:30,080
this is a top-grade
imperial green jade stone

390
00:15:30,390 --> 00:15:32,150
that is auctioned off
for 100 million yuan!

391
00:15:33,840 --> 00:15:34,750
You're giving someone

392
00:15:34,750 --> 00:15:35,910
a gift worth 100 million?

