395
00:15:49,750 --> 00:15:51,410
♪I understood♪

396
00:15:52,500 --> 00:15:56,830
♪That I must confess to you♪

397
00:15:58,790 --> 00:16:02,630
♪My youth and my romance♪

398
00:16:02,820 --> 00:16:05,420
♪Have all flown away with you♪

399
00:16:06,890 --> 00:16:10,630
♪My fantasies and my recklessness♪

400
00:16:10,630 --> 00:16:13,660
♪Have all melted because of you♪

401
00:16:14,940 --> 00:16:18,770
♪My tears and my smile♪

402
00:16:18,770 --> 00:16:21,670
♪Have all been warmed by you♪

